<h3 id="why-i-did-it">Why I did it</h3>

<p>We lost power like 5 times within the first year living hear, more times than anywhere iâ€™ve ever lived. The power lines run through a mass of trees so usually a tree falls on the line and disconnects it from the transformer. The longest we were without power was 3.5 days. Gotta love living in the country. After the 3rd time my dad bought a new generator and gave me his hand-me-down. I have a fair bit of knowledge of</p>
